{"tid":118323,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港主場】2017世界場地單車錦標賽","createTime":"2017-02-13T02:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-13T09:02:50.000Z","uid":38304,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1359fe8b87f048955e13ef1a0ca1777c289424b","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"香港拎到2017單車世錦賽嘅主辦權<br />\n李慧詩當然會出戰 有機會爭到彩虹戰衣<br />\n <br />\n早兩日李慧詩喺亞洲錦標賽贏左三金<br />\n已經係亞洲封王 都見到佢狀態好好<br />\n希望大家可以入場支持下香港隊 <br />\n唔好淨係奧運嗰時先跟風撐下 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017場地單車世界錦標賽<br />\n時間<br />\n<br />\n從&nbsp;4月12日（星期三） / 下午3時正<br />\n<br />\n至&nbsp;4月16日（星期日） / 下午5時正<br />\n<br />\n地區<br />\n<br />\n香港單車館<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳寶康路<br />\n105-107號<br />\n<br />\n價錢: $50-400不等 <br />\n有學生優惠 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ticketflap.com/zh/ucicycling2017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketflap.com%2Fzh%2Fucicycling2017&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewOKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ca886d64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ticketflap.com/zh/ucicycling2017</a><br />\n門票發售緊架喇 有興趣/得閒可以去支持下<br />\n<br />\nbtw 奧運完左 政府講到幾支持香港體育 今次香港主辦世錦賽咁大件事 差唔多冇宣傳過 連傳媒都係2016年 年頭提過下算 連門票開售左都冇乜人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f35fff9622363fecda7feab84dfa659b34d2d1","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b6e2e9c3aec4abcc4c04af2ab5b2bea4685edf","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a725513ee3bc564d9ffb98c4fa66a75665d3327","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507dfbe80885e0e04d23b5e6f1cf9f39b942036f","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd74ae6897f611fb81914e45c13326ecb61834d","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7494bfb9a4e51b8a89ca07c6cf3e8558b85229cd","tid":118323,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T02:49:33.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0bddd89dd385bd9c8afbf015c95c24f61c7c16","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6046a449d2a5bc7f2f4cd38a0aca078d1bddbd19","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb9753de3e2e63a61e7d2d9d911d7330f9d7134","tid":118323,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"會去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5874b76db1e36a4c5fda2ee34c8dba5777f769e8","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:31:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1ca8646bab9978060286c43c94cb2500c39874","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:08:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e88e96e51455bbe9ccbc3065d12d509d6e3599","tid":118323,"uid":38304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T07:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e19dca3d882c6f6c22d0a2a6d748b4f88597412","tid":118323,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"今日星期三，場地單車世錦賽在香港揭幕。去年世錦賽在倫敦，再前一次由倫敦主辦是1904年。前年在巴黎，再前一次在巴黎是1964年。我想說的是：對香港單車隊員來說，今次可能是一世人唯一讓親朋好友主場見證自己出戰世錦賽的機會。對李慧詩媽媽來說，今次可能是她唯一不用追看電視新聞，都能親身緊貼女兒賽果的罕有機會。對我們來說，這可能是唯一在屋企門口主場看世錦賽的機會。這簡直是千載難逢的歷史時刻。倫敦知道，所以去年積極宣傳。英國單車聯會於去年世錦賽前12日宣佈，一連五日共12節門票九節售罄。我知，去年奧運年。我明，所有隊full team。我撐，自己人搞梗撐，但我想問：為何截至開鑼前24小時，香港世錦賽五日共10節（每節不足2,000座位）只得一節爆滿呢？<br />\n<br />\n數字不騙人。上周三晚上8時20至23分，我登陸官方售票網站查看情況並存底。我只記得，那是令人氣結、不忿與心痛的三分鐘。除最後一節外，每節都有位剩，以下是當時順序十節剩餘座位數字：1,577、1,332、1,570、1,048、周五假期開始剩1,468、595、1,299、496、周日剩1,436、26（輪椅位），共剩10,847。以10節不足兩萬張門票來計算，當時售票率不足五成。六日後至周二下午三時，每節仍有1,495、1,149、1,485、752、1,271、105、1,155、61、1,315與24（輪椅）座位，賣剩8,812張門票，總空凳仍接近一半。我不怪總會負責辦賽事的專業人士，他們去年辦過世界盃分站，UCI主席以至車手都激讚組織好；我怪負責宣傳的人。賽前一周屬賣票關鍵，此等宇宙級宣傳六日賣2,035張門票，多謝晒。你對得住長年累月離鄉別井、難得主場比賽的單車隊嗎？說到底，香港運動員deserve better。最後我希望大家買飛，撐自己人。<br />\n文：丹尼爾（陳恩能）"},{"pid":"b815d6d78865f1c39c6cb165b012455e1a554be8","tid":118323,"uid":41714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T05:40:49.000Z","msg":"聽晚自己一個去， 打算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358f5db4b0cc67eddae6f7f0e0e28041af693b93","tid":118323,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"2017年4月13日,星期四<br />\n<br />\n第3節開始時間 15:00<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">女子爭先賽 資格賽，1/16及1/8 </span><br />\n男子凱琳賽 第1輪及遺才賽<br />\n預計結束時間 17:45<br />\n<br />\n第4節開始時間19:00<br />\n女子團體追逐賽 第1輪，決賽及頒獎典禮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">女子爭先賽 1/4</span><br />\n男子凱琳賽 第二輪，決賽及頒獎典禮<br />\n男子團體追逐賽 決賽及頒獎典禮<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">男子捕捉賽 決賽</span>及頒獎典禮<br />\n預計結束時間21:50<br />\n<br />\n港隊重點:<br />\n<br />\n今日 3 PM , 李慧詩  同 馬詠茹   會出戰  女子爭先賽   資格賽 <br />\n今晚 8 PM 之後,  會有 梁竣榮 沖擊 男子捕捉賽決賽"},{"pid":"547b20700dc6183bb6ad5f386e0c7a6e48e9700f","tid":118323,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7502e70e65dc3f37b487760c62fac469bdac9d6e","tid":118323,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"女子爭先賽 資格賽 完結<br />\n李慧詩 第二名晉級 16 強<br />\n馬詠茹 包尾 未能晉級"},{"pid":"6df3ba7a951c3745111c9d91a7fd930bd5e949d4","tid":118323,"uid":41714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"即場 買飛得唔得？"},{"pid":"8829d3b6ea721f9ba0ac1200f1fbee41333acd3f","tid":118323,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:00:54.000Z","msg":"李慧詩其中一個大敵   澳洲 莫頓 輕鬆 擊敗 中國 劉俊紅"},{"pid":"6feb6c64d15fb577d169a5fd5260f61206d2de2b","tid":118323,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"16 強賽<br />\n<br />\n李慧詩 輕取 荷蘭 雲妮絲新   晉級 8 強"}]}